### Installation
1. Read and fix requirements, please see [System Requirements](https://github.com/niksedk/subtitleedit-avalonia#system-requirements)
2. Download the appropriate package for your platform
3. Extract the archive (or use installer if available)
4. Run the executable (on macOS, the app is unsigned - see [System Requirements](https://github.com/niksedk/subtitleedit-avalonia#system-requirements) for how to allow it).

*This is an automated build from the GitHub Actions workflow.*]]></releaseNotes>
